&lt;h2 id="tech-stack"&gt;Tech Stack
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Backend uses Flask + Flask-SocketIO, frontend uses Tailwind CSS + Alpine.js. Real-time log pushing is implemented based on WebSocket.&lt;/p&gt;
